        "title": "Autoplaying carousels",
        "description": "You can make your carousels autoplay on page load by setting the ride option to carousel. Autoplaying carousels automatically pause while hovered with the mouse. This behavior can be controlled with the pause option. In browsers that support the Page Visibility API, the carousel will stop cycling when the webpage is not visible to the user (such as when the browser tab is inactive, or when the browser window is minimized).",
